      "rationale": "Fluent 2022 R2 code verification benchmarks for rotating-reference-frame incompressible flow (lid-driven cavity, Taylor-Couette) are documented in ANSYS verification manual. Results reproduced internally and archived. Achieved level 2 satisfies MRL 2 requirement."
