      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence study on at least three mesh levels with GCI reported for primary QoI.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study (1.2 M / 4.8 M / 19.2 M polyhedral cells) performed at the design operating point. GCI for mean velocity magnitude: 1.4% (fine grid). GCI for pressure head: 2.1%. Monotonic convergence confirmed. Apparent order of accuracy 1.93, consistent with second-order spatial discretisation. Achieved level 3 exceeds requirement."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions documented and shown to bracket clinical operating envelope.",
      "rationale": "In-vitro hemolysis experiments conducted in accordance with modified ASTM F1841 using bovine blood with haematocrit 33±2%. Five flow-speed combinations (2 L/min–3500 RPM, 3 L/min–3000 RPM, 4 L/min–2500 RPM, 5 L/min–2500 RPM, 6 L/min–2000 RPM) span the clinical CPB operating range. Temperature maintained at 37±0.5°C. Test conditions meet level 2 requirement."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metric defined; predicted and measured QoI compared with error metric reported.",
      "rationale": "Mean absolute error (MAE) between predicted and measured normalised plasma-free haemoglobin rise reported as 11.3% across five operating points. RH index comparison uses predicate-normalised metric per FDA guidance. Pressure head comparison within ±5% across HQ curve. Velocity field comparison within 8% RMS. All metrics within pre-specified acceptance bands. Level 2 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
