      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs used in validation are the same as or directly linked to the QoIs used in the COU decision.",
      "rationale": "The primary COU QoI is the relative hemolysis index RH. Validation activities directly measure and predict RH at the same operating points used for the tolerance sensitivity study. Velocity and pressure QoIs are secondary and support mechanistic confidence. Direct traceability between validation QoIs and COU QoIs established. Level 2 achieved."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the validation activities to the COU",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
