      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties and boundary conditions sourced from measurements or validated reference data and documented.",
      "rationale": "Blood viscosity modelled as Newtonian with dynamic viscosity 0.0035 Pa·s and density 1060 kg/m³, consistent with haematocrit 33% literature values. Inlet flow rate boundary conditions set to measured pump bench-test values. Rotational speed set to tachometer-measured values ±0.5 RPM. All input parameters documented in simulation input record. Level 2 achieved."
